---

<main class="pb-8 md:pt-24 md:pb-24">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:justify-center items-center">
    <Picture
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Digital concepts"
      widths={[800, 800, 800]}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  <div>
    <h1
      class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      No more accrocchi!
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      At Dualistic, we advocate simplicity and prioritize workplace wellbeing. 
      Our next-gen Digital Twin platform prioritizes easiness and human-centric design.
    </p>
